title: I Don't Wish You Happy New Year
info:
PC + Atari ST MIDI sync. Vocals are Amiga + Atari.

"I Don't Wish You Happy New Year
Coz anyway this year is shit Ben Laden's still running :
your Game Boy is not safe !
People are going crazy
Mickael Jackson is dead
Do you really think this life is worth living ?
Yes, there's an other world, a little secret garden
Called the Retro Land, where everything's so colorfull
Biatch, we are pixelised but we don't give a flyin' fuck
We are the Outrun gangstas, ghostriding our red car
Rumble pack, wireless pads, analog sticks, what's dat shit ?
We just need A, B, Select, Start, left and right
Too much pixels's bad, that's what your Mama says
Kid you know she's always right, now go and kill your X-Box
Me and my crew are addicted to the Chip Sound
YM and SID, those ones are good for you !
Rumble pack, wireless pads, analog sticks, what's dat shit ?
We just need A, B, Select, Start, left and right ..."
